summary:
PROFESSIONAL EXPERIENCE:

2019-Current Position: International School Breda (The Netherlands)
DP teacher of Mathematics
MYP teacher of Mathematics

2013-2019: International School of Utrecht (The Netherlands)
DP teacher of Mathematics SL & HL
MYP teacher of Mathematics - grades 6 to 10 -
MYP teacher of Spanish - phases 1 to 4 -

2012-2013: Colegio Santa María de El Puig (Spain)
2 months as a cover teacher for Mathematics and Design & Technology.

2011-2012: Wateringse Veld College (Holland)
Taalcoach Spaans.

2009-2013: DelftTetch (Holland)
4 years. 3D model-engineer & laser-scanning 
+ Marketing & Sales.

2008: Jeroen Schipper Architecten bv (Holland)
6 months internship.

2007: Enrique R. Gimeno Arquitecto (Spain)
6 months. CAD-drawing.

2006: Projects Department, Universidad Politécnica de Valencia, E.T.S.A (Spain)
1 academic year. Research project on the development of a town near Valencia.


LANGUAGES:

ENGLISH: High level 
Primary and secondary education in a British school, Caxton College. Advanced Certificate University of Cambridge.

GERMAN: Basic level (A2 certificate)

DUTCH: Basic level
NT2 program, Level 4 (Rotterdamse Volksuniversiteit)

SPANISH: Mother tongue

CATALAN: Medium level


COMPUTING TOOLS:
  ManageBac
  Smart boards
  E-learning platforms: ck-12, KhanAcademy, GeoGebra, Kognity, etc.
  CAD & Design tools: AutoCAD, Photoshop, etc.
  Microsoft Office tools
  Windows & MAC OS
